gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 127, Magic 113
gameRecap.excerpt: Jalen Williams (33 points, 12-18 FG) and Shai Gilgeous-Alexander (32 points, five assists) combine for 65 to lead the Thunder over the Magic, 127-113.  Paolo Banchero tallied 23 points, six rebounds and 10 assists for the Magic in the losing effort.  The Thunder improve to 37-17 on the season, while the Magic fall to 29-25.
